description: Shanna the She-Devil returns in an all-new limited series jam-packed with jungle action, Hong Kong gangsters, dinosaurs, diamonds, and cavemen! Justin Gray and Jimmy Palmiotti reunite with super-hot artist Khari Evans (Daughters of the Dragon) to bring you the story of modern-day pirates shipwrecked on the Marvel Universe's deadliest island, where only Shanna can protect them from hordes of man-eating monsters! Collects Shanna: Survival of the Fittest #1-4.
name: TPB

volume.name: Shanna the She-Devil: Survival of the Fittest

description: The Fantastic Four's life is in turmoil. New threats raise their heads, both outright and some more insidious. Some can be fought with fists, others through the legal system. Facing bankruptcy, Reed must decide the future for his company and his family. In the most turmoil of all is the lovable Ben Grimm, the Thing. Locked in a monstrous body, has he finally found the cure to what has ailed his soul for decades? Collects Fantastic Four (1998) #35-39.
name: Fantastic Four: Flesh and Stone

description: Follow the Fantastic Four from their original adventure to the height of their success! Caught in a mental maelstrom of alien enemies! Trips into the Negative Zone, Subterranea, and the soul of Ben Grimm! The triumph and tragedy of Mr. Fantastic! The FF rescued from Skrullian straits by an all-new lineup! And who will be the last hero standing in the ultimate war...of practical jokes? Featuring Dr. Doom, Dr. Octopus, the Impossible Man, Daredevil, Spider-Man, Wolverine, and more! Collects Fantastic Four #1, #39-40, #51, #100, #116, #176, #236, #267; Fantastic Four (Vol. 3) #56 and #60; Marvel Fanfare #15; Marvel Two-In-One #50; and Marvel Knights 4 #4.
name: Volume One

description: Grant Morrison's best-selling multipart Batman epic continues with this collection of the six-issue miniseries! Witness Bruce Wayne's adventures across time as he is swept through the time stream, from the ancient days that predate history itself through epics set in the times of pirates and the Old West, through his triumphant return to present day Gotham City!
name: HC

volume.name: Batman: The Return of Bruce Wayne - The Deluxe Edition

description: Reprint notes: Black Bob and the Black Prowlers was previously in The Weekly News dated 3/22/1952 to 5/31/1952, Black Bob Book 1957, and issues 990 to 1000 of The Dandy (dated 11/12/1960 to 1/21/1961).
name: Black Prowlers

description: Nathan Never is asked by the attorney Sara McBain at his birthday party at the Hindenburger restaurant  . Shortly before , however , the android Tony dies because of an amoeba " Strikeshape " that someone put in his body: the Strikeshape attacks Nathan , who manages to kill it. But when the agent finally , will rendezvous with Sara , he must face  with a jealous secret admirer ...
name: Una canzone per Sara

description: History shows that in the 1500s, Nostradamus' three volumes of prophecies were best-sellers, making him a rich man. But what the world doesn't know is that he used his vast treasure-trove of riches to create a foundation to prevent his most catastrophic prophesies from occurring! This secret team still functions today, using Nostradamus' published and unpublished tomes to predict threats to worldwide security.

Cover by Geoff Senior. The fabric of space and time is in turmoil. Transformers from two eras collide in an attempt to save the universe! Spinning out from events in Transformers: The Movie. Includes all-new exclusive background material!

Collecting the Time Wars story arc from Marvel UK's The Transformers issues;

  • Worlds Apart! #130-131
  • Dry Run! #189
  • All in the Minds!; Transformers Annual 1989
  • Altered Image!; Transformers Annual 1989
  • Time Wars #199-205
name: Time Wars

description: The   Museum of the Worlds has sent a mission in the tropical forest . Nothing special : just to pick up a bit ' of video material . Pure and simple routine . Still , someone threatens members of the expedition , so we had to ask the assistance of the Alfa . Meanwhile , the mysterious " circles " appear suddenly on the forest floor and all communications ceased abruptly , leaving the expedition members cut off from the rest of the world ...
name: Segnali Dallo Spazio

description: A hospital , a city of small and big pain . Dylan Dog and Madame Trelkovski are trapped in a haunted building , no one can escape from its disturbing Hall , closed forever in darkness. Jealously guards its involuntary guests, painful humanity that desperate struggle, kicking and screaming and then resign ... Waiting patiently for the inevitable apocalypse !
name: Apocalisse

description: Too much television is bad , that's for sure . But there is one channel you can send your brain into orbit or blow it up   , there is only one station that can push you to suicide or murder , there is one powerful signal that can broadcast the ' horror in its purest form ... And it's a channel that you can not change . Dylan Dog holds on the remote , because he knows that in that little box , there is an enormous power ...
name: Canale 666

description:
The night is illuminated by a flash , an object crashed to the ground . The young Amy Irving meets an alien force by the incredible power , the power to shape itself in myriad forms . the mysteries of the entire cosmos 
reveal themselves in front of Dylan Dog .
What is the secret purpose of creation ? Why did you choose the earth ? And because he wants a son to Amy ?
name: Alfa e Omega

description: nuf si htaed ... Yes, sometimes you have to read backwards the book of destiny in order to understand the plot . A chain of deaths without explanation and without blame , hellish monsters coming out of the mirrors , open doors to other worlds . Remember , Dylan ? It all started at the home of Rowena during a masked ball , a dance where no one has what appears to be .
name: Attraverso lo specchio

description: The roar of a motorcycle across the country  , death in the role of a masked rider .  There's an angry look behind his glasses and a homicidal genius moves his fingers . Hazel Dove is tormented by bloody premonitions , she may know to be the next victim . She knows she is the target of a terrible revenge , she hide in the back of the mind the memory of a damned day !
name: Giorno Maledetto

description:
The world's first super-team returns in this volume collecting the first 4 issues of the all-new JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA series, written by Geoff Johns (52, GREEN LANTERN, ACTION COMICS) with stunning art by Dale Eaglesham (VILLAINS UNITED) and Art Thibert (OUTSIDERS) and a cover by Alex Ross (JUSTICE, KINGDOM COME)!

Determined to rebuild the Justice Society, founding members Green Lantern, Flash and Wildcat initiate an unprecedented recruitment program, tracking the bloodlines of heroes across the world and bringing in the new Starman, Damage, Liberty Belle and more! But just as the Society welcomes the rookies into their ranks, an evil force sets out to destroy them. Meet new legacies, solve a mystery stretching into the far future, witness the return of the world's greatest hero and watch another one fall in this fantastic collection!
name: Volume 1

volume.name: Justice Society of America: The Next Age

description: Issue #127
name: neurodeliri

description: Issue #128
name: atroci delitti

description: Collecting 2001's most critically acclaimed Spidey stories! Join writer J. Michael Straczynski (Babylon 5) and penciler John Romita Jr. as an encounter with an enigmatic stranger forever changes the way Peter Parker looks at himself - and his alter ego, the Amazing Spider-Man! Plus, the wall-crawler faces reality head-on as he deals with the worst tragedy ever to befall his city: the events of September 11th! Plus: Paul Jenkins and Mark Buckingham's modern tale of hero worship in the inner city, as well as Greg Rucka and Eduardo Risso's glimpse into the dark life of the Kingpin! Collects AMAZING SPIDER-MAN (Vol. 2) #30-36, SPIDER-MAN'S TANGLED WEB #4-6, PETER PARKER: SPIDER-MAN #36, and ULTIMATE MARVEL TEAM-UP #6-8!
name: Volume One

description: Issue #126
name: la nera vita di linda farrell

description: The second volume of Spider-Man's greatest moments picks up where Vol. 1 left off, collecting the best stories from three Spider-Man series: AMAZING SPIDER-MAN, PETER PARKER: SPIDER-MAN, and SPIDER-MAN'S TANGLED WEB. Volume II features stories written by J. Michael Straczynski and Paul Jenkins, writer of the bestselling ORIGIN! Collects AMAZING SPIDER-MAN #37-45, PETER PARKER: SPIDER-MAN #44-47, and SPIDER-MAN'S TANGLED WEB #10-11.
name: Volume Two

description: The latest volume of the best Spider-Man stories the House of Ideas has to offer presents an entire year's worth of tales from AMAZING SPIDER-MAN - including the monumental reconciliation between Peter and Mary Jane, and an interdimensional invasion that sees Spidey set adrift in the time stream, forced to relive his greatest battles! Featuring the landmark AMAZING SPIDER-MAN #500, this deluxe hardcover culminates in one very special, unexpected reunion! Collects AMAZING SPIDER- MAN #46-58 & 500.
name: Volume Three

description: A stunning new volume collecting JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA #7-12, featuring the prelude to and the first three parts of "Thy Kingdom Come," the sequel to the classic KINGDOM COME! Welcome the newest member to the Justice Society of America: the Kingdom Come Superman! Coming from an Earth plagued by heroes-gone-extreme, how will this Superman react to an incarnation of the Justice Society he never knew?
name: Part One

volume.name: Justice Society of America: Thy Kingdom Come

description: The Kingdom Come Superman continues to crusade against evil alongside his new Justice Society teammates – but is he the only one who can stand against the threat of Magog? And what are Gog's true motives? This hard-hitting new volume collects JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA #13-18!
name: Thy Kingdom Come: Part Two

volume.name: Justice Society of America: Thy Kingdom Come

description: Collecting JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA #19-22, and the JUSTICE SOCIETY: KINGDOM COME Specials MAGOG, SUPERMAN and THE KINGDOM! Picking up where PART II left off, the Justice Society begins to dissolve as Gog vows to bring peace to Earth in a way that frightens some and thrills others. Torn between Gog's desire to help the world and the moral cost it comes with, it's old guard vs. the new as the line that was drawn is crossed.
name: Thy Kingdom Come: Part Three

volume.name: Justice Society of America: Thy Kingdom Come

description: It's the year 2504. In the aftermath of an apocalyptic war, the surviving humans are ruled by the Beasterians, animal-human hybrids created to be the ultimate soldiers, but who instead became merciless tyrants. Doomed to extinction, humanity's future rests with the savior whose birth is foretold by the Post-Testament Bible.
name: Vol. 1

description: One of the classic Alan Moore works is finally back in print in this new full color, magazine size, printing with totally re-mastered artwork and lettering. As Alan Moore himself says " A Small Killing is one of the best pieces of comic book art that I have ever been involved in." Adman Timothy Hole has everything going for him and has now been handed the biggest assignment of his life, marketing a major cola in Russia. But his smooth life begins to unravel as he is stalked by a demonic child that makes him question not just who he is, but how he really effects those around him. It is about the little murders that we all have to make each day just to get by. The trace assassinations of tiny things. Really, how much damage can be done by a small killing? This work is much more than a sophisticated thriller, it is a nonlinear masterpiece, from the writer who has defined adult graphic novels! As an added bonus this graphic novel includes a new commentary article by both Alan Moore and the artist Oscar Zarate.
name: A Small Killing

description: The All-Stars survive their first major battle against an army of super-foes in this first JSA ALL-STARS volume collecting issues #1-6, but in the aftermath, one team member is missing. The mysterious Strike Force has taken that member captive – and there's someone else who wants the missing hero even more.
name: Constellations

description: As a result of the destruction of the Alfa Agency Headquarters, the commissioner of the Agency , Solomon Darver assumes command and begins the reconstruction of the new Alfa Building. Meanwhile , Sigmund , not entirely convinced of the authenticity of the movie that shows the death of Reiser , seeking help from Igor McNally to verify possible counterfeits.
name: Dalle Ceneri

description: Continue in this issue and end the long adventure that saw Nathan Never confront a gang of smugglers in the hell of the Territory. While on the trail moves the Yakuza , Sykes , leader of the Night - runners , he prepares himself   to make the last race . But Nathan  will first deal with the  sect  of  "Recuperanti", a group of fanatics of "The God Machine" .
name: Punto Zero

description: The young Peter King , a descendant of a family of wealthy industrialists , is kidnapped after a bloody firefight . His captors demand a exorbitant ransom, that the family is disposed to pay. Ensure that everything goes the right way ask for help to Alfa Agency , but things fall and the life of Peter seems little more hanging by a slender thread .
name: Citta Violenta

description: Nathan , that was once a police officer , now returns to wear the uniform . This is not a return to origins , but a undercover investigation into a police station , District 22, to shed light on the death of an agent, considered the hero of the neighborhood. The case appears closed when it captured the son of a famous local boss.
name: Codice Zero

description: Nathan Never is sent on Titan, Saturn's third moon , where it is installed an Earth outpost , in search of a missing ship . But when he and his traveling companions arrive near their destination , that's strange phenomena begin to occur . These are mere hallucinations or something more ? And what are the mysterious machinery constantly active in the base on Titan ?
name: Il Mistero della Terza Luna

description:
"I know your secret."

Tonight is Tommy Morris's big chance: he's been invited to party with the social elite of Franklin High and maybe even hook up with the girl of his dreams. But when a prank call turns sour, Tommy gets much more than he bargained for . . .

The Secret is a chilling coming-of-age mystery from Dark Horse founder Mike Richardson and Eisner-nominated artist Jason Alexander (Damn Nation; The Escapists).
name: I Know Your Secret

description:
The mystery of Pam's disappearance deepens as police link it to another unsolved crime.

The Secret is a chilling coming-of-age mystery from Dark Horse founder Mike Richardson and Eisner-nominated artist Jason Alexander (Damn Nation, The Escapists).

A series of wrong turns has brought Tommy to the steps of a rundown farmhouse in the middle of nowhere . . . and the car belonging to Pam's kidnapper.

The Secret is a chilling coming-of-age mystery from Dark Horse founder Mike Richardson and Eisner-nominated artist Jason Alexander (Damn Nation, The Escapists).

Tommy and Kyle have snuck inside the decrepit farmhouse where they hope to find some sign of Pam, who was abducted a year ago. When the ominous figure unexpectedly returns, they discover what he keeps in his horrific basement-and they're trapped in the middle.

The Secret is a chilling coming-of-age mystery from Dark Horse founder Mike Richardson and Eisner-nominated artist Jason Shawn Alexander (Damn Nation, The Escapists).

Thomas Weiss is a chemist and worked in a hospital in White City , in the

east continent . In this city the crime dominates and the population is threatened by the dangerous " Scramble " , mutant monsters that crawl under the snow. When Nathan reached the place for the investigation, he is accompanied by a colleague of Thomas , the Dr. Diane Weston , a doctor telepath ...
name: La Morte Bianca

description: Alfa agents , aided by Sonia Merida an amateur meteorology , began to investigate to discover which are the secret plans of the powerful Skotos , which , thanks to the control of the weather , now seems ready to unleash a " Universal flood " on Earth in order to destroy all all forms of life and give the planet to its formidable techno-organic creatures called "Tecnodroids" . Meanwhile , in the palace of Skotos , continue the experiments on " Neos ", the first natural Tecnodroid that , now an adolescent , is beginning to become familiar with his powers .
name: Tecnodroidi

description: The insidious witch doctor Ew Chott Channy has completed his wicked voodoo curse--the War on Flesh--and he is eager to unleash it upon the world. But time is against him... Sergot, a determined leader from an ancient tribe, can postpone the apocalypse and spare the world an eternity locked in a season of death. But the evil transcends time, and the dark forces root within a young boy whose destiny can cast a permanent shadow on all of mankind. A vicious swarm of Ew Chott hornets makes way for an army of the walking dead...and thus begins a declaration of war on the living, a war on all souls, and a war on flesh!
name: Vol. 1

description: In a decaying mansion in the blackest heart of the Louisiana bog, Drake uncovers more secrets of the Six... and angers a spirit that wants to ensure the gunslinger never leaves the swamp alive! It's man versus some of the meanest man-eaters to ever crawl out of the marsh!
name: Crossroads Part Two

description: After fighting Black Lantern Ted Kord, Booster Gold finds himself lost in time, struggling to save his sister Goldstar from imminent death. However, when Booster rescues her from the timestream, he realizes that the sister he saved is not the same girl he remembers. Collecting BOOSTER GOLD #26-31.
name: Volume 5

description: Join CLIFFJUMPER and ARCEE as they battle their way through DECEPTICON forces in a desperate adventure to learn the secrets of Space Bridge Technology! STARSCREAM, the DECEPTICON enforcer stands in their way, not just from the mission, but to rejoin OPTIMUS PRIME and his AUTOBOTS as well! This is the PREQUEL to the new hit TV Show!

Some of the world s best manga creators join together to bring the world of Warcraft to life as never before! Between these covers lie tales of adventure treachery humor and bravery. Told from both Alliance and Horde point of view these stories have entertained the likes of travelers soldiers and thieves. They have endured the trials of time and have earned the title of legend.

Contents

  • Fear
  • Warrior: Divided
  • Miles To Go
  • Family Values
name: Vol. 2

description: Some of the world's best manga creators join together to bring the world of Warcraft to life as never before! Between these covers lie tales of adventure, treachery, humor and bravery. Told from both Alliance and Horde point of view, these stories have entertained the likes of travelers, soldiers and thieves in taverns, inns and camps all throughout Azeroth. They have endured the trials of time and have earned the title of legend. Whether this is your first journey into Azeroth, or merely the latest in a long line of visits, this collection will not soon be forgotten!
name: Vol. 4

description: When the Twolegs destroy the warrior Clans' forest home, Graystripe--second in command of ThunderClan--is captured while trying to help his comrades escape! However, Graystripe soon discovers that the captive life as a pampered kittypet isn't all that bad. The cozy Twoleg nest and his new, affectionate family help Graystripe put his Clan days behind him. Still, nothing compares to the life of a warrior! With a new kittypet ally, Millie, by his side, will Graystripe ever find his way back to the Clan?
name: The Lost Warrior

description: Graystripe and Millie's journey to find ThunderClan has only just begun when the pair is faced with a series of obstacles that seem insurmountable. Getting out of Twolegplace alive isn't nearly as simple as expected, and Millie's unfamiliarity with life in the wild makes it a challenge for Graystripe to keep them both moving forward. But just when a temporary refuge is in sight, conflict with a tribe of barn cats threatens to break the travelers apart for good!
name: Warrior's Refuge

description:
Graystripe and Millie have finally found ThunderClan's old territory, but Twoleg monsters have devastated the forest and Graystripe fears that all of his Clanmates have been killed or captured by Twolegs. Millie insists that they keep looking, and an old friend helps point the two cats on the path that the Clans followed many moons ago.

But danger still lurks around every turn, and Graystripe worries that he and Millie are lost on an impossible journey.
name: Warrior's Return

description:
'Survival of the fittest' is a universal truth, one that Toma learns the hard way outside of the classroom. Chosen to fight on behalf of Earth in an interplanetary tournament, Toma realizes that the loser will end up as dead meat--literally! According to the universal plan, there will be 'Feeders' and there will be 'Food,' with the beings of one world feeding on the blood and meat of others. Only one planet can survive... Who will be on the menu?

Chapter Titles

  • Episode 1 - I What?!
  • Episode 2 - The Rules of War
  • Episode 3 - Enter: The Hardcore Wanderer [Axel Potter - Part 1]
  • Episode 4 - The Soldier Teacher [Axel Potter - Part 2]
  • Episode 5 - Karma's Assassin [Axel Potter - Part 3]
  • Episode 6 - One Last Test [Axel Potter - Part 4]
  • Episode 7 - Invoking the Codon [Axel Potter - Part 5]
name: Vol. 1

description: Karma deploys two Earth gladiators - the dangerously gorgeous and seductive Locutus and by-the-book hitman Leon--to assassinate Toma. Even though Toma may be able to fend of his attackers, will he be able to overcome temptation in order to spare the life of Itsuki, the girl of his dreams? It's a no-holds-barred intergalactic street brawl, and the bloodshed is just beginning!
name: Vol. 2

description: Let's get ready to rum-m-m-m-m-ble! It's a free-for-all battle to the end between Toma, B. J. Leon, Axel Potter and Locutus. The location: a deserted spaceship in a hostile, desolate world. Karma is now heading to this rendezvous point after capturing Itsuki. During the battle, B. J. goes for the heart...and tries to take control of Itsuki!
name: Vol. 3

description: In the final blood-soaked volume of Warriors of Tao, the gladiators go for the jugular in an attempt to quench their insatiable appetite for destruction--and survival. Toma, Locutus and Axel corner Karma, who has abducted Itsuki and begins to drain her will to live. In the heat of battle, the group's anger and rage only serve to strengthen Karma! With no hope in sight, Toma has no choice but to make the ultimate sacrifice...
name: Vol. 4

description: The war between Earth and orbiting stations is unstoppable , wherever they open up new fronts and all the contenders have begun to move their pawns with feverish strategies . Meanwhile , Nathan Never and his colleagues of Alfa Agency have reached the destinations assigned to them by Nadia Galya , head of the Earth Security Council.
name: Il Giorno degli Eroi

description:
The Nathan task force , led by Senator Sawyer , has now come to the conclusion that the billionaire Neil Bates , head of one of the most powerful industries specializing in research on genetic engineering , is involved in the mysterious death of district attorney Mc Bain . While Nathan and his friends are preparing to enter the headquarters of Bates , Sawyer ,already seriously ill,  
has a dangerous crisis. The operation seems hopelessly compromised .
name: L'ultimo Addio
